\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 My biggest fear growing up were monsters\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  As adults our fears tend to progress\'85most of us aren\'92t afraid of monsters anymore but we all deal with fear on daily basis.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 WE\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What if \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My kids don\'92t turn out the way I want\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I lose my job\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The economy never recovers\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I get sick or something bad happens to my spouse\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Someone finds out my secret\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I never find the one to be with for the rest of my life\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Fear and Anxiety can be debilitating!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Write down on the card your biggest fear!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  This morning I want to look at a guy who was afraid of something that made no sense.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 GOD\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs36 \cf4 19\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 Now Ahab told Jezebel\'a0everything Elijah had done and how he had killed\'a0all the prophets with the sword.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah has just had this huge victory where three signs happen to prove God is with him.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He stopped it from raining for years.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He called down fire from heaven and then killed all the prophets from the opposing team.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He called for it to rain and it did.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So in the test of the power of the god\'92s and who is bigger and stronger it wasn\'92t even close.  Jezebel\'92s gods are pathetic\'85Elijah\'92s God is the big winner and in control!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So Jezebel sent a messenger to Elijah to say, \'93May the gods deal with me, be it ever so severely,\'a0if by this time tomorrow I do not make your life like that of one of them.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Hold up, time out\'85which gods is she talking about?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}She is threatening Eli here with vow based on the gods who were just whipped by Eli.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Lady you are crazy!!!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This statement makes no logical sense\'85and that is really what so many of the threats that come our way are\'85illogical things that people say or we feel that put us in a state of fear.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So what does the hero of the story do?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 3\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Elijah was afraid
\fs15 \super [\ul a\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0and ran\'a0for his life.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This makes no logical sense\'85God just got done protecting him and doing this amazing thing in his life and now he running from a woman with what are either simple empty threats or the delusions of a mad person.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I think back to all the times where empty threats have captivated me in my life.  Where I forget what God has done in my life and through me and run and hide from whatever comes my way.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 22\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Do not merely listen to the word, and so deceive yourselves. Do what it says.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 23\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Anyone who listens to the word but does not do what it says is like someone who looks at his face in a mirror\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 24\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and, after looking at himself, goes away and immediately forgets what he looks like.\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For years I thought of this passage as only for improvement and to better ourselves.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But this past week I started to look at it differently\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What if what God is telling us is not just get better and do better! \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That is what so much preaching and teaching is today in the church. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s self help and pick up your boots straps and do better\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Work harder \'96 which leads to guilt and shame and frustration in everyone\'92s life.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 25\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But whoever looks intently into the perfect law that gives freedom,\'a0and continues in it\'97not forgetting what they have heard, but doing it\'97they will be blessed in what they do.  James 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have to live in fear\'85you can live in freedom!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it\'92s found by not forgetting that \'91God says He will!\'92\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He will protect you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He will love you no matter what\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He will provide for you\'85maybe not in the way you want but He will provide for you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He will never leave you nor forsake you!  Ever!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92re free!  Go live in that freedom\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  But like so many times in my life \'96 Eli forgot what God had done in his life already.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf4 When he came to Beersheba\'a0in Judah, he left his servant there,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub while he himself went a day\'92s journey into the wilderness. He came to a broom bush,\'a0sat down under it and prayed that he might die.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Wait\'85he just ran away because he was afraid to die didn\'92t he?  Yeah.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But I think maybe there is also something deeper going on too!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe Elijah was also tired of fighting.  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Initially he was scared to die which sent him running.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But I believe part of him left because he was just tired.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s the fear of never having rest\'85never having peace\'85looking at your life and thinking\'85is this really all I have to live for?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This happens all the time in marriages!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s terrifies me to thinking I\'92ll spend the rest of my life in this terrible state of conflict and fighting and I don\'92t care what God says or has done\'85I\'92d rather that dream die!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But it isn\'92t just marriages\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s things we pray for and hope for and the loss or frustration in not getting what we want just makes us want to check out.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s children we pray for to come home \'96 spiritual or physically or emotionally.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s what I talked about last week with jobs\'85and getting rejected week after week\'85and you\'92re done!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of Robin Williams committing suicide\'85not sure what battles he was fighting but he was done.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Every day we fight battles \'96 and there is temptation in all of us to want to quit fighting for what God has put in our hearts\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4  \'93I have had enough,\'a0Lord,\'94 he said. \'93Take my life;\'a0I am no better than my ancestors.\'94\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Then he starts to get spiritual and deep \'96 I\'92m no better than anyone else\'85just end it God!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then he lay down under the bush and fell asleep.  All at once an angel\'a0touched him and said, \'93Get up and eat.\'94\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I LOVE this verse!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Eli is throwing this serious temper tantrum and running from God and rejecting the calling on his life and everything God wants to do with him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And God\'92s response is \'85um\'85I think you need snickers bar\'85you\'92re not yourself when your\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He looked around, and there by his head was some bread baked over hot coals, and a jar of water. He ate and drank and then lay down again.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The angel of the\'a0Lord\'a0came back a second time and touched him and said, \'93Get up and eat, for the journey is too much for you.\'94\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So he got up and ate and drank. Strengthened by that food, he traveled forty\'a0days and forty nights until he reached Horeb,\'a0the mountain of God.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub There he went into a cave and spent the night.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That must have been one powerful meal to last that long!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was like a super snickers on steroids or something.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 And the word of the\'a0Lord\'a0came to him: \'93What are you doing here, Elijah?\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What are you doing here?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is inviting him into a conversation \'96 the voices you listen determine the  future you experience!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Again God isn\'92t condemning to Elijah\'85He\'92s questioning!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of me being depressed for a week and knowing what to do though\'85God was asking me \'96 What are you doing here, Nic?\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  Then after God asks him a second time, because God wasn\'92t amused with his first response\'85.he says this.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 14\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He replied, \'93I have been very zealous for the\'a0Lord\'a0God Almighty. The Israelites have rejected your covenant, torn down your altars, and put your prophets to death with the sword. I am the only one left, and now they are trying to kill me too.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Eli\'92s assessment of the situation isn\'92t accurate as we find out later but that is how he feels.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He feels like the only one!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Feelings can create disillusionment - Acted on disillusionment can create disaster\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 15\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The\'a0Lord\'a0said to him, \'93Go back the way you came, \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
